context: <user>  I need to take a train from cambridge, I need to arrive at my destination by 17:00/ <system>  Okay, what day did you have in mind? <user>  I would like to leave on Saturday. <system>  What station would you like to arrive at? <user>  I need to get to Norwich please. <system>  TR3823 will arrive at 16:55, would that work for you? <user>  That cuts it a little close but it will do. I don't need it booked, though. Can you also find me a place to get some food? <system>  I sure can! Do you have a specific area and type of food you are looking for?<user>  I would like an indian restaurant in the centre, please. <system>  I have many. is there a price range that you prefer?<user>  Whichever ever one has 11:00 for two people on the same day available, that one would be fine. <system>  I was able to book a table for 2 at Curry Garden on Saturday at 11:00. The reference number is 0ZBV3E4C . Is there anything else we can help you with?<user>  No that will be all. Thanks for your help! <system>
